<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
<head>
  <title>plone.reload</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
</head>
<body>

    <h1>plone.reload</h1>

    <div style="background-color:#eee; padding:0.5em; line-height:1.2em;">
        Note: plone.reload is still experimental and some functionality is
        not yet as good as it can be. Current limitations include:
        <ul style="margin:0.5em;">
            <li>
                You need to 'reload' your code once for plone.reload to track
                it. Do that before doing the first changes to it, but after it
                has been loaded, i.e. put into sys.modules.
            </li>
            <li>
                Currently plone.reload doesn't reload any decorated methods
                correctly, so apply decorators (like the ones from
                plone.memoize or property) once finished with your code.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <tal:block tal:condition="view/status">

        <h2>Status</h2>

        <pre tal:content="view/status"
             style="background-color:#ddd; padding:0.5em;
                    border: 1px black dashed; line-height:1.2em;">
            Status
        </pre>

    </tal:block>

    <h2>Actions</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:3px;">
                <form action="#" tal:attributes="action request/getURL" method="get">

                    <input type="hidden" name="action" value="code" />

                    <input type="submit" value="Reload Code" />

                </form>
            </td>
            <td style="padding:3px;">
                <form action="#" tal:attributes="action request/getURL" method="get">

                    <input type="hidden" name="action" value="zcml" />

                    <input type="submit" value="Reload Code and ZCML" />

                </form>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>
</html>
